```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Owner {
        +String name
    }

    class Pet {
        +String name
        +Owner owner
    }

    class Schedule {
        +String name
        +Owner owner
    }

    class Task {
        +int duration
        +String priority
        +String item
    }

    Owner "1" --> "1" Pet : owns
    Pet "1" --> "*" Schedule : has
    Schedule "1" --> "*" Task : includes
```
